				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/參"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#xF96B;</span></a><a href="/whv/㕘"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x3558;</span></a><a href="/whv/䫩"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x4AE9;</span></a><a href="/whv/㽩"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x3F69;</span></a><a href="/whv/㺑"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x3E91;</span></a><a href="/whv/㠁"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x3801;</span></a><a href="/whv/㜗"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x3717;</span></a><a href="/whv/㓄"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x34C4;</span></a><a href="/whv/𧑁"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x27441;</span></a><a href="/whv/𪅩"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2A169;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩴑"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x29D11;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩌰"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x29330;</span></a><a href="/whv/𩅙"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x29159;</span></a><a href="/whv/𨝐"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x28750;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦌀"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x26300;</span></a><a href="/whv/𥊀"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x25280;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤨵"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x24A35;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤗲"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x245F2;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤍜"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2435C;</span></a><a href="/whv/𣯶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x23BF6;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢿈"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x22FC8;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢕕"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x22555;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠬙"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x20B19;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠗿"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x205FF;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠔭"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2052D;</span></a><a href="/whv/黲"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x9EF2;</span></a><a href="/whv/鰺"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x9C3A;</span></a><a href="/whv/鬖"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x9B16;</span></a><a href="/whv/驂"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x9A42;</span></a><a href="/whv/鏒"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x93D2;</span></a><a href="/whv/醦"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x91A6;</span></a><a href="/whv/遪"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x906A;</span></a><a href="/whv/贂"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8D02;</span></a><a href="/whv/謲"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8B32;</span></a><a href="/whv/襂"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8942;</span></a><a href="/whv/蔘"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8518;</span></a><a href="/whv/縿"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7E3F;</span></a><a href="/whv/糝"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7CDD;</span></a><a href="/whv/篸"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7BF8;</span></a><a href="/whv/穇"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7A47;</span></a><a href="/whv/磣"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x78E3;</span></a><a href="/whv/瘮"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x762E;</span></a><a href="/whv/犙"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x7299;</span></a><a href="/whv/滲"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6EF2;</span></a><a href="/whv/毿"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6BFF;</span></a><a href="/whv/槮"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x69EE;</span></a><a href="/whv/摻"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x647B;</span></a><a href="/whv/慘"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x6158;</span></a><a href="/whv/幓"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5E53;</span></a><a href="/whv/嵾"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5D7E;</span></a><a href="/whv/墋"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x588B;</span></a><a href="/whv/嘇"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5607;</span></a><a href="/whv/剼"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x527C;</span></a><a href="/whv/傪"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x50AA;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
